    {
      "id": "69d90412db4b02ec42f728eb",
      "text": "謎解き2026-04-04",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf450",
      "text": "from [2026/04/05]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf451",
      "text": "[謎解き]2026-04-04",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830116
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf452",
      "text": "　>[Shiroikaibutsu_ https://x.com/Shiroikaibutsu_/status/2040376547442581575] note謎「徒花」のクイズを作りました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830046
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041b00000000000bf464",
      "text": " > ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830046,
      "updated": 1775830046
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041b00000000000bf465",
      "text": " > 先生に計算プリントを渡すようだけど…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830046,
      "updated": 1775830046
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041b00000000000bf466",
      "text": " > ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830046,
      "updated": 1775830046
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041b00000000000bf467",
      "text": " > 今回は1つの謎が隠れているよ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830046,
      "updated": 1775830046
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041b00000000000bf468",
      "text": " > [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFDfp0QaUAAy2Za?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830046,
      "updated": 1775830046
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf453",
      "text": "　　わからん！[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830052
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf454",
      "text": "　　わからん[yosider.icon][caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf455",
      "text": "　　諦めて[Claude Opus 4.6]にぶち込んだら(ほぼ)解いた！すごい[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf456",
      "text": "　　\tがちか[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf457",
      "text": "　　\t　すごい[nishio.icon][imo.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf458",
      "text": "　　\t僕のClaudeたんはお手上げだった[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf459",
      "text": "　　\t\t>この謎解き、かなり難しいですね！もしゲームのタイトルや他のヒントがあれば、もう少し絞り込めるかもしれません。何かわかっている情報はありますか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf45a",
      "text": "　　\t\tそうなのか ちなみに自分は拡張思考ONでやった[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf45b",
      "text": "　　\t\t\t拡張思考初耳だった、そんな機能があったとは！[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf45c",
      "text": "　　[~ まずは一番上の数式だけで考えるのがいいかも[yosider.icon]]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf45d",
      "text": "　　 [~ その法則を上から3つ目の数式で検証する]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf45e",
      "text": "　　[~ 一番上の数式の読み方は「ごわるきゅう」[yosider.icon]]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf45f",
      "text": "　　わが家のclaudeも解けた（opus拡張）[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf460",
      "text": "   [謎ときをするclaude]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf461",
      "text": "　　みんなClaudeでやってるから帰ったらChatGPTで試す[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775830035
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9041000000000000bf462",
      "text": "\t\tChatGPTにヒントを出してもらってるけど全然わからない[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775830035,
      "updated": 1775832527
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90a8a00000000002cfd90",
      "text": "\t\t\tそもそも正しくヒントを出しているのか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775831691,
      "updated": 1775831702
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90a9600000000002cfd91",
      "text": "\t\t\t全然正しくなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775831702,
      "updated": 1775832399
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90d4e00000000002cfd93",
      "text": "\t\t\t数字は画数とか言ってた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775832399,
      "updated": 1775832413
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90d5e00000000002cfd94",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[~ 画数で特定できるか〜？と思って数字1文字が一文字になる他の方法を考えて]、解けた✅",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775832414,
      "updated": 1775832497
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90d8c00000000002cfd95",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[~ 間違ったヒントだけど、画数4の木に関係するもの、木だよね]、というのはヒントになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1775832460,
      "updated": 1775832506
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90a9600000000002cfd92",
